Package model

Class Plant

java.lang.Object
model.Item
model.Plant
public class Plant extends Item
The Accessory class is a sublclass of the Item class. It holds all information about an Accessory item and provides functionality specific to Accessories. The Accessory class adds the 'accessoryType' field to represent the type of accessory it is
